\begin_layout Subsubsection
Bushfire activity records
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The bushfire activity records are the same as those used in the previous
 chapters.
 The two datasets were produced by the Department of Environment, Land,
 Water and Planning (DELWP) of Victoria and Risk Frontiers (RF).
 Both datasets are comparable using events greater than 10.000 Ha as the
 threshold to define bushfire events.
 The selected period of analysis using this definition was 1961-2010.
 The datasets have a greater correlation during this time.
 Chapter 4 discusses further details about these datasets.
\end_layout

